---
// src/pages/index.astro
---
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>Chicken Cost Club | Calculate Your Poultry ROI</title>
		<style>
			:root { --barn-red: #7C0A02; --grass-green: #2d5a27; }
			body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background: #fdfbf7; color: #333; margin: 0; text-align: center; }
			header { background: var(--barn-red); color: white; padding: 3rem 1rem; border-bottom: 5px solid var(--grass-green); }
			.card { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); max-width: 600px; margin: 2rem auto; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
			h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 2.5rem; }
			.btn { background: var(--grass-green); color: white; padding: 1rem 2rem; border: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<header>
			<h1>Chicken Cost Club</h1>
			<p>Modern Tools for the Homestead</p>
		</header>
		<div class="card">
			<h2>The Red Barn ROI Calculator</h2>
			<p>Your Alpha site is now live. We are initializing the interactive vault logic next.</p>
			<div style="background: #eee; padding: 2rem; border: 2px dashed #ccc; margin: 1.5rem 0;">
				[ Calculator Initializing... ]
			</div>
			<a href="https://news.chickencost.com" class="btn">Join the $10 Founder's Club</a>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
